#etcsl: line-id=A.A.16

17. me nam-en-na ba-ab-[...]
#lem: me[Being]; namen[the office of en-priest]; X
#etcsl: line-id=A.A.17

18. ŋi₆-par₄-ra dib-dib-be₂ [... ...]
